            <div id="dsq-comment-message-877" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>Hey there! Tim Smith here, the lead designer of this game, and a member of Gentleman Squid Studio. Thanks for taking the time to review our game. So glad you enjoyed it! One thing I would love to point out is that while we don&#8217;t have a level select feature, there *is* the option to replay a level when presented with your score, so if you didn&#8217;t get that perfect run-through you were aiming for, you can try the level again right away until you are satisfied with your performance. Thankis again for some positive press :)</p>
</div>
