            <div id="dsq-comment-message-878" class="dsq-comment-message"><blockquote><p>there *is* the option to replay a level when presented with your score</p></blockquote>
<p>True. Not having a level select is both a good and a bad thing though, because once you&#8217;ve moved past a level, there&#8217;s no way to go back and try to &#8217;100% it&#8217;, to maximize available skill points. That said, I&#8217;m sure most people won&#8217;t mind, since like you said, one can retry the current level again and again, until a satisfactory result is achieved, so its absence is not <i>really</i> an issue.</p>
